
<body style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px;">
    <div class="container bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm" style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto;">
        <div class="text-center bg-success text-white py-3 rounded-top">
            <h2>Order Confirmation</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{CustomerName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your order has been successfully placed!</p>

            <ul class="list-group mb-3">
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{OrderId}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Total Amount:</strong> ${{TotalAmount}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Order Date:</strong> {{OrderDate}}</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Thank you for ordering from us. We appreciate your business and hope you enjoy your purchase!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center text-muted small pt-3 border-top">
            &copy; 2025 YourCompany. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

